# Normalize line endings in the repo. Added 2026-07-15 after Windows-side tooling
# rewrote oms/service.py + session-handoff.md with CRLF, turning a 176-line semantic
# change into a 9022-line diff and making PR #464 -- a live-money stop-path change --
# effectively unreviewable. Text files are stored LF in git regardless of platform.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.csv text eol=lf
